videos.headline: Corral's INT woes continue with a pick in the end zone
videos.description: Matt Corral ends Ole Miss' drive without any points as he throws an interception in the end zone to Auburn DB Roger McCreary.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Corral's INT woes continue with a pick in the end zone) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bigsby goes up the middle for an Auburn TD
videos.description: Tank Bigsby takes the handoff and runs up the gut to open the scoring for Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bigsby goes up the middle for an Auburn TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss answers with a short TD
videos.description: Elijah Moore gets some space and grabs the 6-yard touchdown to get Ole Miss on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss answers with a short TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nix keeps it on the option and jogs into the end zone
videos.description: Bo Nix fakes the handoff, then strolls for six points to put Auburn back on top.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nix keeps it on the option and jogs into the end zone) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Williams clears his defender with a hurdle
videos.description: Seth Williams leaps over his defender on a 21-yard gain, which would lead to an Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn's Williams clears his defender with a hurdle) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss' fancy fake FG does not end well
videos.description: Ole Miss' holder flips the ball over his head to the kicker, but he gets tackled well short of the first-down marker.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss' fancy fake FG does not end well) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Corral gets popped after second rushing score of game
videos.description: Matt Corral once again keeps the ball and scores before taking a shot after getting in the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Corral gets popped after second rushing score of game) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bigsby delivers big stiff-arm en route to a TD
videos.description: Tank Bigsby lives up to his first name with a crushing stiff-arm before scoring the Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bigsby delivers big stiff-arm en route to a TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ealy's rushing score puts Ole Miss back on top
videos.description: Jerrion Ealy goes straight up the middle on the handoff and scores from five yards out to give the Rebels a 1-point lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ealy's rushing score puts Ole Miss back on top) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams throws up the deuces on Auburn's go-ahead TD
videos.description: Auburn retakes the lead for good as Bo Nix connects with Seth Williams for a 42-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams throws up the deuces on Auburn's go-ahead TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET
